    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AdminHomePage
    AdminHomePage class represents the user interface for the admin user.
    AdminSetupPage
    The AdminSetupPage class handles the setup process for creating an administrator account.
    Answer
    Represents an answer to a question in a QandA application.
    AutomatedTestCaseQuestionAnswer
    A utility class for creating and running automated test cases.
    AutomatedTestCaseQuestionAnswer.TestCase
    Interface for defining test cases.
    AutomatedTestCaseQuestionAnswer.TestResult
    Represents the result of a test case execution.
    ChatDetailWindow
    ChatDetailWindow class displays the detailed view of a chat conversation, allowing users to view message history and send new messages.
    DatabaseHelper
    The DatabaseHelper class is responsible for managing the connection to the database, performing operations such as user registration, login validation, and handling invitation codes.
    DatabaseHelperDM
    The DatabaseHelperDM class is responsible for managing the direct messaging functionality in the database, including chat creation, message sending, and message retrieval.
    DatabaseHelperReviews
    This class handles the database operations related to trusted reviewers functionality.
    DirectMessage
    DirectMessage class represents the interface for viewing and interacting with direct messages from other users.
    DirectMessage.ChatListCell
    Custom cell renderer for chat list items.
    DirectMessage.ChatListItem
    Inner class to represent a chat list item.
    FirstPage
    FirstPage class represents the initial screen for the first user.
    InstructorHomePage
    InstructorHomePage class represents the user interface for the instructor user.
    InstructorPromote
    InstructorPromote class represents a pop-up window that allows instructors to promote or demote students by adding or removing the reviewer role.
    MyReviewsPage
    This class provides functionality to view all reviews created by the current user.
    PasswordEvaluator
    Title: Directed Graph-translated Password Assessor.
    QandAPage
    This page handles all Question and Answer functionality, including displaying, creating, updating, and voting on questions and answers.
    Question
    Represents a question in a QandA application.
    QuestionValidator
    Validator class for Questions and Answers.
    QuestionValidator.ValidationResult
    Helper class that encapsulates the result of a validation operation.
    Review
    Represents a review for an answer in the question and answer system.
    ReviewerHomePage
    This class represents the home page for a reviewer user in the application.
    ReviewValidator
    A utility class that provides validation for review texts.
    ReviewValidator.ValidationResult
    An inner class that represents the result of a validation operation.
    ReviewWindow
    This class handles the Review Window functionality, including displaying, creating, updating, and deleting reviews, as well as marking reviewers as trusted and voting on reviews.
    SetupAccountPage
    SetupAccountPage class handles the account setup process for new users.
    SetupLoginSelectionPage
    The SetupLoginSelectionPage class serves as the entry point to the application's authentication system.
    StaffDmView
    StaffDmView class represents an interface for staff members to view direct messages between users in the system.
    StaffDmView.ChatListCell
    Custom cell renderer for chat list items in the staff view.
    StaffDmView.ChatListItem
    Inner class to represent a chat list item in the staff view.
    StaffDmView.StaffChatDetailWindow
    Inner class for displaying a chat detail window for staff monitoring.
    StaffHomePage
    StaffHomePage provides a graphical interface for staff users after login.
    StaffUserDelete
    StaffUserDelete class represents the user interface for staff members to manage users.
    StartCSE360
    Main application class that serves as the entry point for the CSE360 application.
    User
    The User class represents a user entity in the system.
    UserHomePage
    UserHomePage provides a graphical interface for student users after login.
    UserMuteManager
    UserMuteManager provides functionality for staff to manage user mute settings.
    UserNameRecognizer
    Title: FSM-translated UserNameRecognizer.
    WelcomeLoginPage
    The WelcomeLoginPage class displays a welcome screen for authenticated users.
